{
  "id": "/subscriptions/ce4a7590-4722-4bcf-a2c6-e473e9f11778/resourceGroups/pstestrg2/providers/Microsoft.Storage/storageAccounts/stopstestrg2/inventoryPolicies/default",
  "name": "DefaultInventoryPolicy",
  "type": "Microsoft.Storage/storageAccounts/inventoryPolicies",
  "properties": {
    "lastModifiedTime": "2023-10-11T07:10:08.7152211Z",
    "policy": {
      "enabled": false,
      "type": "Inventory",
      "rules": [
        {
          "destination": "containerpstestrg2",
          "enabled": false,
          "name": "test1",
          "definition": {
            "format": "Parquet",
            "schedule": "Weekly",
            "objectType": "Blob",
            "schemaFields": [
              "Name",
              "Creation-Time",
              "Last-Modified",
              "Content-Length",
              "Content-MD5",
              "BlobType",
              "AccessTier",
              "AccessTierChangeTime",
              "Metadata",
              "AccessTierInferred",
              "Tags",
              "Snapshot",
              "VersionId",
              "IsCurrentVersion"
            ],
            "filters": {
              "creationTime": {
                "lastNDays": 3
              },
              "blobTypes": [
                "blockBlob",
                "appendBlob"
              ],
              "prefixMatch": [
                "abc",
                "edf",
                "eqwewqe",
                "eqwewqreewqe",
                "qwewqewqewqewqewadasd"
              ],
              "includeBlobVersions": true,
              "includeSnapshots": true
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "destination": "containerpstestrg2",
          "enabled": false,
          "name": "test2",
          "definition": {
            "format": "Csv",
            "schedule": "Daily",
            "objectType": "Container",
            "schemaFields": [
              "Name",
              "Metadata",
              "PublicAccess",
              "Last-Modified",
              "LeaseStatus",
              "LeaseState",
              "LeaseDuration",
              "HasImmutabilityPolicy",
              "HasLegalHold",
              "Etag",
              "DefaultEncryptionScope",
              "DenyEncryptionScopeOverride"
            ],
            "filters": {
              "prefixMatch": [
                "con1",
                "con2"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "destination": "containerpstestrg2",
          "enabled": true,
          "name": "test3",
          "definition": {
            "format": "Csv",
            "schedule": "Weekly",
            "objectType": "Blob",
            "schemaFields": [
              "Name",
              "Deleted",
              "RemainingRetentionDays",
              "Content-Type",
              "Content-Language",
              "Cache-Control",
              "Content-Disposition"
            ],
            "filters": {
              "includeDeleted": true,
              "excludePrefix": [
                "aaa1",
                "bbb1"
              ],
              "blobTypes": [
                "appendBlob"
              ],
              "prefixMatch": [
                "abc1",
                "edf1"
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
